# Project Standards

- Use Next.js 14 App Router
- TypeScript strict mode mandatory
- No client-side API fetching
- All data must come from local JSON files
- Keep components modular
- Avoid large components (>150 lines)
- Use Tailwind only for styling
- Use Recharts for charts
- Highlight years 2008, 2012, 2020, 2022
- Prioritize readability over animations
- Write clean and professional code
- No any types allowed
